import React from 'react';
import Box from '@mui/material/Box';
import Grid from '@mui/material/Grid';
import ReadTable from './ReadTable';



function DailyTaskForm(props) {

    const [inputarr,
        setInputarr] = React.useState([])

    const [inputdata,
        SetInputdata] = React.useState({
            task_name: "",
            category: "",
            jira_id: "",
            Assignee: "",
            Status: "",
            due_date: "",
            go_live: "",
            mock_up: "",
            other_comments: ""
        })

    function handleChange(e) {

        SetInputdata({
            ...inputdata,
            [e.target.name]: e.target.value
        })

    }

    let { task_name,
        category,
        jira_id, Assignee,
        Status,
        due_date,
        go_live,
        mock_up,
        other_comments } = inputdata;
        function changhandle() {
            setInputarr([
                ...inputarr, {
                    name,
                    rollNo
                }
            ])
    
            console.log(inputdata, "input data what we Enter")
            SetInputdata({name: "", rollNo: ""})
    
        }
        return (
            <>
                <Box className='section'>
                    <Box className='container task-form'>
                        <Grid container spacing={2}>
                            <Grid item md={5} >
                                <input type="text" name='task_name' onChange={handleChange} value={taskdata.task_name} placeholder='Task Name' />
                            </Grid>
                            <Grid item md={5}>
                                <select name="category" value={taskdata.category} onChange={handleChange}>
                                    <option value="">Select Cotegory</option>
                                    <option value="Nap Bug Task">Bug Task</option>
                                    <option value="Nap Dev">Dev</option>
                                    <option value="Nap Dev">staging</option>
                                </select>
                            </Grid>
                            <Grid item md={2}>
                                <input type="text" onChange={handleChange} value={taskdata.jira_id} name='jira_id' placeholder='Jira ID' />
                            </Grid>
                        </Grid>
                        <Grid container spacing={2} mt={1}>
                            <Grid item md={3} >
                                <select name="Assignee" value={taskdata.Assignee} onChange={handleChange}>
                                    <option value="">Select Assignee</option>
                                    <option value="Rohan">Rohan</option>
                                    <option value="Kriti">Kriti</option>
                                    <option value="Archana">Archana</option>
                                </select>
                            </Grid>
                            <Grid item md={3}>
                                <select name="Status" value={taskdata.Status} onChange={handleChange}>
                                    <option value="">Select Status</option>
                                    <option value="Completed">Completed</option>
                                    <option value="Pending">Pending</option>
                                    <option value="Processing">Processing</option>
                                </select>
                            </Grid>
                            <Grid item md={3}>
                                <input type="date" value={taskdata.due_date} name='due_date' onChange={handleChange} />
                            </Grid>
                            <Grid item md={3}>
                                <input type="date" value={taskdata.go_live} name='go_live' onChange={handleChange} />
                            </Grid>
                        </Grid>
                        <Grid container spacing={2} mt={1}>
                            <Grid item md={12}>
                                <input type="textarea" value={taskdata.mock_up} name='mock_up' onChange={handleChange} placeholder='Mock UP' />
                            </Grid>
                        </Grid>
                        <Grid container spacing={2} mt={1}>
                            <Grid item md={12}>
                                <textarea name='other_comments' value={taskdata.other_comments} onChange={handleChange} placeholder='Other Comments' rows="4" />
                                <button onClick={changhandle}>Submit</button>
                            </Grid>
                        </Grid>
                    </Box>
                </Box>
                <ReadTable inputarr={inputarr} />
            </>


        );
    }

export default DailyTaskForm;
